---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/layouts/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="The Big Picture | Home Performance Stakeholder Council"
	description="Learn about the science of home performance and how the HPCN network was developed for industry, by industry to advance home performance standards in British Columbia."
	keywords="home performance, whole-home approach, HPSC, HPCN, building envelope, mechanical systems, British Columbia"
>
	<Breadcrumbs
		items={[
			{ label: 'About', href: '/about' },
			{ label: 'The Big Picture', href: '/about/the-big-picture' },
		]}
	/>

	<!-- Page Header -->
	<div class="mb-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Big Picture</h1>
		<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-4xl">
			Understanding home performance and how the HPCN network is advancing the industry across
			British Columbia.
		</p>
	</div>

	<!-- About Home Performance -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<div
			class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primary/5 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border-2 border-primary/20"
		>
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Home Performance</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
				Home performance is the science of improving homes using a <strong
					>whole-home approach</strong
				>. This means looking at the entire system—not just individual components—to understand
				how they work together.
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<div
						class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
					>
						<svg
							class="w-7 h-7 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Building Envelope</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
							Walls, windows, doors, roof, and foundation working together
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<div
						class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
					>
						<svg
							class="w-7 h-7 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"
							></path>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Mechanical Systems</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">HVAC, ventilation, and other home systems</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<div
						class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
					>
						<svg
							class="w-7 h-7 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Occupant Behavior</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">How people use and interact with their home</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<div
						class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
					>
						<svg
							class="w-7 h-7 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Environmental Conditions</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Climate, weather, and local environment</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-primary">
				<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
					The goal: Make homes <span class="text-primary">safe</span>,
					<span class="text-primary">comfortable</span>,
					<span class="text-primary">efficient</span>, and
					<span class="text-primary">durable</span>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Background -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Background</h2>
		<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
				The concept for the Home Performance Contractor Network emerged from the <strong
					>HPSC Working Roadmap</strong
				>, a collaborative effort to advance home performance standards across British Columbia.
			</p>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
				The network was developed through extensive consultation with industry stakeholders:
			</p>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 my-8">
				<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-primary/20 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
						<svg
							class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Interviews</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Stakeholder consultations</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-primary/20 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
						<svg
							class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Workshops</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Collaborative sessions</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-primary/20 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
						<svg
							class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Conference Calls</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Regular discussions</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-primary/20 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
						<svg
							class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
							fill="none"
							stroke="currentColor"
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						>
							<path
								stroke-linecap="round"
								stroke-linejoin="round"
								stroke-width="2"
								d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"
							></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Surveys</h3>
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Industry feedback</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Development -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Network Development</h2>
		<div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border-l-4 border-primary">
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
				<strong>Developed for industry, by industry.</strong> The HPCN criteria and standards were
				created by Sector Councils representing key trades across the home performance industry.
			</p>

			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Sector Councils</h3>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Fenestration</span>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">HVAC</span>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Insulation</span>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Renovation</span>
				</div>

				<div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg">
					<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
						<path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Energy Advisors</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- HPCN and Rebate Programs -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">HPCN and Rebate/Incentive Programs</h2>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
			<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md border-2 border-primary/20">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Central Database</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					The HPCN provides a <strong>central database of accredited contractors</strong> that
					utilities and government programs can access to find qualified professionals for their
					rebate and incentive programs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md border-2 border-primary/20">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Program Independence</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					Utilities and government continue to <strong>run their own incentive programs</strong>.
					Contractors must still meet specific program requirements in addition to HPCN
					accreditation.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Looking Ahead -->
	<section class="mb-16">
		<div
			class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-dark rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white"
		>
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Looking Ahead</h2>
			<div class="space-y-4 text-white/95 text-lg leading-relaxed">
				<p>
					The Home Performance Contractor Network is not static—it will <strong
						>evolve and expand over time</strong
					> to meet the changing needs of the industry and homeowners across British Columbia.
				</p>
				<p>
					We are committed to <strong>ongoing evaluation and stakeholder engagement</strong> to
					ensure the network continues to advance industry priorities and maintain the highest
					standards of quality.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
				<a
					href="/contractor-network"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white text-primary rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
				>
					Learn About the Network
					<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
					</svg>
				</a>
				<a
					href="https://app.registeredbccontractor.ca/profiles"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
				>
					Apply Now
					<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"
							stroke-width="2"
							d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"
						></path>
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
